#: ../../manual/lighting/lamps/area.rst:28
msgid ""
"Note that the :guilabel:`Distance` setting is much more sensitive and "
"important for :guilabel:`Area` lamps than for others; usually any objects "
"within the range of :guilabel:`Distance` will be blown out and overexposed. "
"For best results, set the :guilabel:`Distance` to just below the distance to"
" the object that you want to illuminate."
