#: ../../manual/lighting/lamps/area.rst:33
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Area` lamp doesn't have light falloff settings. It uses an "
"\"inverse quadratic\" attenuation law. The only way to control its falloff "
"is to use the :guilabel:`Distance` and/or :guilabel:`Gamma` settings."
msgstr ""

